import React from 'react'
import DrawerComp from '../../Components/DrawerComp/DrawerComp'
import {
  Drawer,
  DrawerBody,
  DrawerFooter,
  DrawerHeader,
  DrawerOverlay,
  DrawerContent,
  DrawerCloseButton,
  useDisclosure,
  Flex, Box, Spacer, Text, Stack, Radio, RadioGroup, CheckboxGroup, Checkbox,
} from "@chakra-ui/react"
import { ArrowBackIcon } from '@chakra-ui/icons'
import Ripples from 'react-ripples'

const ChooseLastItemDrawer = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <DrawerComp  
      placement={'bottom'}
      bg="black"
      height="20vh"
      borderTopRightRadius='0px'
      borderTopLeftRadius="0px"
      toggleDrawer={true}>
  <DrawerHeader borderBottomWidth="1px">
         
        </DrawerHeader>
        <DrawerBody>
          <Flex justifyContent="space-evenly" alignItems="center">
          <Ripples className="ripple-display">
            <Box w="40%" m="auto" p="10px" bg="#28a745" color="white"><Text color="white">I'LL CHOOSE</Text> </Box>
            </Ripples>
            <Ripples className="ripple-display">
            <Box w="40%" m="auto" p="10px" bg="#28a745" color="white"><Text color="white">REPEAT LAST</Text></Box>
            </Ripples>
          </Flex>
        </DrawerBody>
    </DrawerComp>
    </>
  )
}

export default ChooseLastItemDrawer
